## Context

The Express API currently has no authentication system. All write endpoints (POST/PUT/DELETE) are unprotected and default `userId` to `1`. The task requires adding JWT-based auth: registration, login, token-protected routes, and ownership enforcement. The `jsonwebtoken` package is already installed. Tests are pre-written in `tests/auth.test.ts` and define exact expected behavior.

